text: Crossotus xanthoneurus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Sama in 2000. It is known from Egypt, Jordan and Israel.BioLib.cz - Crossotus xanthoneurus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2000
